========================================================================================

[b][color=#adff2f][size=3][u]What does it do?:[/u][/size][/color][/b]

Changes the default textures of [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53237]Teeth Plus[/url].

- Less White Teeth.
- No more Red/Pink inside of the mouth.
- Adds Shadow Effects like with the Vanilla Mouth.

========================================================================================

[color=greenyellow][size=3][u][b]Installation:[/b][/u][/size][/color]

1) Download and Install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53237]Teeth Plus[/url] by urgarulga first. (doesn't matter which version you pick)
2) Download one of the files from this Mod with NNM.
3) Activate and "Yes" when asked to overwrite.

Done!

========================================================================================

[color=greenyellow][size=3][u][b]Credits and Special Thanks:[/b][/u][/size][/color]

urgarulga for [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53237]Teeth Plus[/url]
